Program: imgpad - pad images
Programmer: R. G. Marson
Date: 24 Sept 1992
Purpose: Pad images with zero in a variety of ways.

Details: Unlike padim this always puts the image in the center
regardless of the ref value.


.INFO
Image, C, 1, Input image
Output, C, 1, Padded output image
Padsize, I, 7, Size of output image
Padval, R, 1, Padding value
.DEFAULT
Image = 
Output = 
Padsize = 256, 256, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1
Padval = 0.0
.END
